    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Because the error you're getting is <strong>not</strong> related to an <code>EditText</code>, then it's <strong>not</strong> related to your keyboard.</p>\n\n<p>The errors you are getting are not a result of your code; you probably are testing on a Samsung device that has Samsung's TouchWiz.</p>\n\n<p>I had the same errors, then I tested on a Nexus S (also by Samsung, but pure Android OS without TouchWiz) and I didn't get this error.</p>\n\n<p>So, in your case, just ignore these errors while testing on a device! :)</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 388878,
      "reputation" : 449,
      "user_id" : 1315117,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/288d4e810d131b39808d22e7eac786a9?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Sachin Shelke",
