    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>On your android phone go to:<br>\n<strong>settings -> application manager -> all -> samsung keyboard and then click on \"clear cache\"</strong><br>\n(delete all data collected by this application).</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
