    "answer_id" : 18229574,
    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Make clear you have pass a value in your MainAcitivity for the following methods onCreateOptionsMenu and onCreate</p>\n\n<p>In some cases, the developer deletes the \"return  super.onCreateOptionsMenu(menu)\" statement  and changed to \"return  true\".</p>\n"
  }, {
