    "answer_id" : 21053559,
    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Check if you have any element such as button or text view duplicated (copied twice) in the screen where this encounters. I did this unnoticed and had to face the same issue.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3318580,
      "reputation" : 9,
      "user_id" : 2790276,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/bGPFy.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Qu&#226;n L&#234;",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2790276/qu%c3%a2n-l%c3%aa"
