    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : -1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1411577210,
    "creation_date" : 1411577210,
    "answer_id" : 26022300,
    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I ran into this problem too when I copied some text from the Internet. My solution is to trim the text/remove formatting before doing any further processing. </p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 5784890,
      "reputation" : 2422,
      "user_id" : 4564450,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 62,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/7orB445e.png?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Andrey Solera",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/4564450/andrey-solera"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : -1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1427591348,
    "creation_date" : 1427591348,
    "answer_id" : 29324530,
    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had the same problem but with a listView.... i solved it because i was using a wrong R.id.listView that list View needed to have a value, in my case it was strings that i saved on listView2... so the right code was R.id.listView2</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 8944678,
      "reputation" : 2178,
      "user_id" : 6672577,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/hpNEb.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Shahzad Afridi",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/6672577/shahzad-afridi"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : -1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1474702941,
    "creation_date" : 1474702941,
    "answer_id" : 39673864,
    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had the same problem then i fixed it by following code!</p>\n\n<pre><code>  text = (EditText)findViewById(R.id.TextVoiceeditText); \n  text.setInputType(InputType.TYPE_CLASS_TEXT|InputType.TYPE_TEXT_FLAG_NO_SUGGESTIONS);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 12401592,
      "reputation" : 39,
      "user_id" : 9038591,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6187b8a01afd3f54606b7f2f6285f0f9?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
