    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : -1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1524910181,
    "creation_date" : 1524910181,
    "answer_id" : 50075335,
    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>this error also occurs due to changed API URL. try hitting the URL you are using in postman and c if it's working properly.\nrechecking the APIs solved my problem</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 7486904,
      "reputation" : 368,
      "user_id" : 5689801,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6a45582032b8a696ce212164e3534e7e?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Eshan Chattaraj",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/5689801/eshan-chattaraj"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : -1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1528290996,
    "creation_date" : 1528290996,
    "answer_id" : 50721466,
    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>try avoiding use of <strong>view</strong> in xml design.I too had the same probem but when I removed the view. its worked perfectly.</p>\n\n<p>like example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>             &lt;EditText\n                android:layout_width=\"match_parent\"\n                android:layout_height=\"wrap_content\"                   \n                android:hint=\"Username\"\n                android:inputType=\"number\"                   \n                android:textColor=\"#fff\" /&gt;\n\n            &lt;view\n                android:layout_width=\"match_parent\"\n                android:layout_height=\"1dp\"\n                android:background=\"#f9d7db\" /&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>also check and try changing by trial and error <strong>android:inputType=\"number\"</strong> to <strong>android:inputType=\"text\"</strong> or better not using it if not required .Sometimes keyboard stuck and gets error in some of the devices.</p>\n"
  }, {
