    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 7818044,
      "reputation" : 49,
      "user_id" : 5912024,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://graph.facebook.com/1020430961332533/picture?type=large",
      "display_name" : "Rahul Nehul",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/5912024/rahul-nehul"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1537622575,
    "last_edit_date" : 1537622575,
    "creation_date" : 1532269188,
    "answer_id" : 51466019,
    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<blockquote>\n  <p>This worked for me...on every device</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<pre><code>    &lt;EditText\n        android:maxLines=\"1\"\n        android:layout_width=\"match_parent\"\n        android:layout_height=\"match_parent\"\n        android:textSize=\"15sp\"\n        android:layout_centerVertical=\"true\"\n        android:textColor=\"#000\"\n        android:id=\"@+id/input_search\"\n        android:background=\"@null\"\n        android:inputType=\"text\"\n        android:hint=\"Enter Address, City or Zip Code\"\n        android:imeOptions=\"actionSearch\"\n        /&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>In Java code:</p>\n\n<pre><code>mSearchText.setOnEditorActionListener(new TextView.OnEditorActionListener() {\n\n        @Override\n        public boolean onEditorAction(TextView textView, int actionId, KeyEvent keyEvent) {\n            if(actionId == EditorInfo.IME_ACTION_SEARCH\n                    || actionId == EditorInfo.IME_ACTION_DONE\n                    || keyEvent.getAction() == KeyEvent.ACTION_DOWN\n                    || keyEvent.getAction() == KeyEvent.KEYCODE_ENTER){\n\n                //execute our method for searching\n            }\n\n            return false;\n        }\n    });\n</code></pre>\n"
