    "question_id" : 13670374,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case, the EditText fields with inputType as <strong>text / textCapCharacters</strong> were casing this error. I noticed this in my logcat whenever I used backspace to completely remove the text typed in any of these fields.</p>\n\n<p>The solution which worked for me was to change the inputType of those fields to <strong>textNoSuggestions</strong> as this was the most suited type and didn't give me any unwanted errors anymore.</p>\n"
  }, {
